name: SARAFI THE GIRAFFE
description: Introducing Sarafi the Giraffe, the tallest meme coin in the crypto savanna! With its head in the crypto clouds and feet firmly planted on the blockchain, Sarafi towers above the competition. Whether you're reaching for moon leaves or just grazing on gains, this long-necked legend is here to bring laughter, community, and un-giraffe-ted potential to your portfolio.
